-- Alessandro Benetton to Replace Father as Chairman, Corriere Says
-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 2012-04-22T10:30:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-22/alessandro-benetton-to-replace-father-as-chairman-corriere-says.html
Benetton Group SpA (BEN)  Chairman Luciano Benetton will be replaced in his role by his son Alessandro,
according to an interview with  Corriere della Sera .  Luciano Benetton told the daily he will leave the positions
he holds in the company on April 24.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
